"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(DISTINCT loan.loan_id)\nFROM loan\nJOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id\nWHERE loan.amount >= 250000\n  AND account.frequency = 'POPLATEK MESICNE'\n  AND loan.date BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1997-12-31';\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the number of distinct loans that meet the specified criteria: loans of at least 250,000, associated with accounts that have chosen monthly statement issuance, and approved between January 1, 1995, and December 31, 1997."